        </div>
        <div class="section-body">
          <div style="background: #EFF6FF; border: 2px solid #2563EB; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px;">
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px;">
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1E40AF;">Format Structure</div>
                <div style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px;">[Year][Program][Type][Sequence]</div>
                <div class="text-xs" style="color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.6;">
                  • Year: Last 2 digits (e.g., 25 for 2025)<br/>
                  • Program: 3-letter code (e.g., ENG, CSE)<br/>
                  • Type: 1=UG, 2=PG<br/>
                  • Sequence: 3-digit number (001-999)
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1E40AF;">Examples</div>
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #BFDBFE; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                  <div style="font-family: monospace; font-weight: 600; color: #2563EB;">25ENG1001</div>
                  <div class="text-xs" style="color: #6B7280;">UG Engineering Student - First in sequence</div>
                </div>
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #BFDBFE; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                  <div style="font-family: monospace; font-weight: 600; color: #2563EB;">25CSE2015</div>
                  <div class="text-xs" style="color: #6B7280;">PG Computer Science - 15th student</div>
                </div>
                <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #BFDBFE; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px;">
                  <div style="font-family: monospace; font-weight: 600; color: #F59E0B;">25ENG1123/A</div>
                  <div class="text-xs" style="color: #6B7280;">Mid-semester joiner format</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="alert alert-info" style="margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 0;">
              <i data-feather="info" style="width: 20px; height: 20px;"></i>
              <div><strong>Important:</strong> Numbers are assigned in alphabetical order of student names. Same ERN is retained throughout the course (except UG → PG transition).</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
